QuestData.Title: Feeding Time is Over
QuestData.Description:
A crucial element to a successful Fearstalk is our tool: the fangs of a terrorbeast.
Their fangs are perfect for revealing the scent of their prey once bound to a soul. There's plenty of them in the forest surrounding the ripening souls.
Go and collect some from their corpses. Their population is a bit large right now anyhow.
QuestData.LogDescription: Kill Winged Terrorbeasts and collect $1oa of their fangs.
